{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"@keyframes shimmer-c{0%{background-position:-400px 0}100%{background-position:400px 0}}\n        .sk-violet{background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(139,92,246,0.12) 25%,rgba(139,92,246,0.22) 50%,rgba(139,92,246,0.12) 75%);background-size:800px 100%;animation:shimmer-c 1.6s infinite linear;border-radius:8px;}\n        .sk-blue{background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(59,130,246,0.1) 25%,rgba(59,130,246,0.2) 50%,rgba(59,130,246,0.1) 75%);background-size:800px 100%;animation:shimmer-c 1.6s infinite linear;animation-delay:0.1s;border-radius:8px;}\n        .sk-amber{background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(245,158,11,0.1) 25%,rgba(245,158,11,0.2) 50%,rgba(245,158,11,0.1) 75%);background-size:800px 100%;animation:shimmer-c 1.6s infinite linear;animation-delay:0.2s;border-radius:8px;}\n        .sk-green{background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(34,197,94,0.1) 25%,rgba(34,197,94,0.2) 50%,rgba(34,197,94,0.1) 75%);background-size:800px 100%;animation:shimmer-c 1.6s infinite linear;animation-delay:0.3s;border-radius:8px;}\n        .sk-c-text{background:linear-gradient(90deg,#e8eaed 25%,#f2f3f5 50%,#e8eaed 75%);background-size:800px 100%;animation:shimmer-c 1.6s infinite linear;border-radius:8px;}\n      \n      \n      \n      \n        \n          \n          \n          \n        \n        \n          \n          \n          \n        \n        \n          \n          \n          \n        \n        \n          \n          \n          \n        \n      \n      \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n      \n    \n    \n      C — Colour-tinted Shimmer\n      Same shimmer wave as A, but each stat card's skeleton uses its actual accent colour (violet, blue, amber, green). Feels like the content is \"almost there\". More expressive but slightly busier.","choice":"tinted","id":null,"timestamp":1781282817986}
