{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"/* Moderate: slight overshoot ~6px then settles */\n        @keyframes moderate-loop {\n          0%,10%  { opacity:0; transform: translateY(18px) scale(0.96); }\n          55%     { opacity:1; transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.01); }\n          70%,90% { opacity:1; transform: translateY(0px) scale(1); }\n          100%    { opacity:0; transform: translateY(18px) scale(0.96); }\n        }\n        .lp-moderate { animation: moderate-loop 3.2s ease-out infinite; }\n        .lp-moderate.d1 { animation-delay: 0s; }\n        .lp-moderate.d2 { animation-delay: 0.09s; }\n        .lp-moderate.d3 { animation-delay: 0.18s; }\n        .lp-moderate.d4 { animation-delay: 0.27s; }\n      \n      \n        \n        142\n        Products\n      \n      \n        \n        2,481\n        Users\n      \n      \n        \n        7\n        Pending\n      \n      \n        \n        3\n        Payments\n      \n    \n    \n      B — Moderate iOS ✦ Recommended\n      Gentle overshoot then settles. Natural, alive — the iOS 26 \"system spring\". Stiffness ~200, damping ~20. Enjoyable first time, not annoying on repeat visits. Scale + translate together.","choice":"moderate","id":null,"timestamp":1781283104158}
